4 zentrale ansätze (laut paper weishen si overview channel assignment...):
	CLICA schwierig mit multiplen radio
	BFS-CA
	INSTC löst auch k-connected(survival feature)aber all nodes must have same number of radios
	CTA

laut jos buch interessant:
rbab06 - ramachandran beldgin interference-aware channel assignment in multi-radio wireless mesh networks -BFS-CA
akt04 - raniwala architecture and algorithms for assignment and routing 
